default3. Reason for submitting evidence:default&#xa0;
default3.1 Given the fact that QLA is a pioneer in this field in Lao PDR, it was of outmost importance for us to share our views. Besides, Lao PDR being the most affected country in terms of cluster munitions contamination, this was also an opportunity for us to call
default for 
default synergies to be made between victim assistance and the broader disability and development frameworks
default -
default to make sure that there exist specific policies for survivors, especially thanks to victim assistance provisions in the Oslo and the Ottawa treaties
default;
default but also 
defaultto make sure 
defaultthat PWD, and thus including survivors, can benefit from the efforts that are made for the development of a country or of a region. Indeed, achieving our goals in term of development is illusory if PWD, including survivors and other vulnerable persons are left behind
default,
default as  has been recalled recently at the highest level with the report of the High 
defaultL
defaultevel 
defaultP
defaultanel
default, 
default th
defaultat
default  of the UN Secretary General
default;
default and  the discussions around the post 2015 agenda.
default&#xa0;
default3.2 
defaultThe Lao PDR is a least developed country experiencing poverty. The country is ranked 133 out of 177 nations in the Global Development index. Approximately 23% of the population lives on less than $1USD per day. Persons with disabilities are particularly vulnerable to poverty  in society. The Lao National Growth and Poverty Eradication Scheme (2003) reported physical and mentally handicapped/blind groups represent the highest percentage (18.5%) of people  at-risk of poverty in Vientiane Municipality. Lack of awareness and understanding by government policy makers and officials lead
defaults
default to exclusion of persons with disability from development programs
default 
defaultD
defaultue to cluster munitions and other UXO 
defaultthere were 
defaultat least 50
default,
default525 mi
defaultne/
defaultERW
default casualties, including 29,506 people killed and 21,
default019 injured since 1964
default. Knowing those figures, it is obvious any initiative taken now
default,
default to 
defaultcreate 
default a society which is inclusive of PWD and where a broad range of services are accessible to all
default,
default will benefit  future generations and will have long lasting effects for themselves but also for their communities since they are, on 
defaultan 
defaultequal basis to others, actors of change.
default&#xa0;
default3.3 Besides, I am myself a person with disability and I have met the barriers I am trying, as the executive director of QLA, to break. I was lucky to find support and to be able to continue my education and then get a job as it is sadly not the case for all PWD, including survivors who remain the poorest amongst the poor because they often do not have access to such services and opportunities. For instance in my own province there is right now only one Rehabilitation centre in Xiengkhouang city which provide
defaults
default such services like rehabilitation, prosthetic and orthotic to survivors and PWD by the CMR and COPE. It is far from most villages where survivors and PWD live and therefore very difficult to access it. For instance my friendwas injured in the 
default1970s 
default when she was sixteen. And she finally received 
defaulther prosthesis on 4
defaultth
default April 2010 with the support of Handicap International and COPE. I would wish 
defaultthat 
defaultall survivors and PWD 
defaultquickly 
defaultaccess quickly 
defaultthe 
defaultsupports we need
default,
default because it means we can survive as human being. I am also part of a survivor initiative called the Lao Ban Advocates and this experience, thanks to a close collaboration with the Lao Government, including with the NRA, has proved to be efficient. We have been working hand in hand with various stakeholders to raise the voice of survivors and their affected communities
default,
default and to help the government in elaborating a framework for addressing their needs. Such 
defaultan 
defaultexample demonstrates that the motto “Nothing about us without us” is a meaningful one and that joint efforts lead to great results.
